headline.print_headline: Wawrinka Fights Back to Beat Federer in Monte Carlo Final
headline.main: Wawrinka Fights Back to Beat Federer in Monte Carlo Final

lead_paragraph: Stanislas Wawrinka signaled his French Open ambitions by beating Roger Federer 4-6 7-6 (5) 6-2 in an all-Swiss Monte Carlo Masters final on Sunday.
